name: Cat Wif Hat
description: CWH (Cat Wif Hat) is a meme token built on Solana, inspired by the whimsical idea of a cat wearing a hat. Combining humor, simplicity, and community-driven engagement, CWH captures the playful spirit of internet meme culture. As a CTO (Community Take Over) project, all decisions are made through shared efforts by the community, emphasizing decentralization, creativity, and inclusivity. CWH stands out as a unique and entertaining addition to the Solana ecosystem.
